  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00646:db7b96ba0457]]\n此前的场景 Skill 集群把正确性、来源、推导、实验和文风放在同一执行链中。它能避免把错误内容润色得更像论文，但不能被称为[[PROTECTED:F00001-P00647:92c2b1b497ad]]。本轮据此新增独立的 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P00648:0262fc49d5f2]]，旧质控集群保持不变。",
  "read_only_context_before": "完整分类边界见 [academic_scenario_classification_report.md]([[PROTECTED:F00001-P00641:4f97fd1cb9e0]])，独立规则、案例、模式、Playbook 和验证门见 [academic_scene_skill_cluster_report.md]([[PROTECTED:F00001-P00642:0badc5a0e7dd]])。",
